:The Lie algebra formula_242 cannot be broken into pieces in the way that the previous examples can: it is &quot;simple&quot;, meaning that it is not abelian and its only ideals are 0 and all of formula_242.

* Another simple Lie algebra of dimension 3, in this case over formula_194, is the space formula_254 of 2 x 2 matrices of trace zero. A basis is given by the three matrices
